		"ITM_TTL_ITEM_LOCATION_SPECIFICTRIPLERANDOMSTATS": "El Castillo Cariñoso",
		"ITM_EXP_ITEM_LOCATION_SPECIFICTRIPLERANDOMSTATS": "Le SALON DE MERCH donnera le TRIPLE des stats à n'importe quel joueur... mais la stat est tirée au pif.",
		"ITM_TTL_ITEM_LOCATION_RANDOMSTATSDICE": "Classy Colosseum",
		"ITM_EXP_ITEM_LOCATION_RANDOMSTATSDICE": "The COMMUNITY ZONE is now married to fortune: upon entering, the amount of a stat players receive will be decided by a die roll.",
		"ITM_TTL_ITEM_LOCATION_DOUBLESTATS": "Sensual Sydney Opera House",
		"ITM_EXP_ITEM_LOCATION_DOUBLESTATS": "THE LOBBY will now provide DOUBLE the stats for any player.",
		"ITM_TTL_ITEM_LOCATION_ALLBUTONENOSTATS": "Gorgeous Great Wall of China",
		"ITM_EXP_ITEM_LOCATION_ALLBUTONENOSTATS": "Only the HOTEL will provide stats. The rest of the locations will not provide stats for any player after choosing them. (The stats given at the end of an event remain the same).",
		"ITM_TTL_ITEM_AUDIO_FORCEDSONGFORPLAYER_PANCAKE": "The Star",
