		"ITM_TTL_ITEM_STATSTOEVERYONE": "The Combat-Ant",
		"ITM_EXP_ITEM_STATSTOEVERYONE": "Everyone's stats are affected by everyone's choices. You must cooperate now.",
		"ITM_TTL_ITEM_TIMEBASEDCHANGEALLSTATSRANDOM": "Kate-rpillar",
		"ITM_EXP_ITEM_TIMEBASEDCHANGEALLSTATSRANDOM": "Every turn, the amount of your STATS change randomly until you choose a LOCATION.",
