		"ITM_EXP_ITEM_TIMEBASEDLOSERANDOMSTAT": "Every turn, you will keep losing STATS until you choose a LOCATION.",
		"ITM_TTL_ITEM_TIMEBASEDSWAP2RANDOMSTATS": "The Battle Beetle",
		"ITM_EXP_ITEM_TIMEBASEDSWAP2RANDOMSTATS": "Every turn, your own STATS will keep swapping positions until you choose a LOCATION.",
		"TTP_PHONENPC_OTHERPLAYER": "Another player has already called this guest!",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_SAWYER": "SAWYER, TELL US: WHAT IS YOUR TYPE?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_SAWYER": "Well... the one thing I yearn for is a simple, quiet existence. I see some of my friends talk about chasing the \"thrills of life\", and... that's just not me? It'd be nice to meet someone who prefers peace for a change.",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_MIRANDA": "MIRANDA, TELL US: WHAT IS YOUR TYPE?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_MIRANDA": "The old Miranda would've said \"a Prince Charming\", mayhaps. But I've grown since the old days. New Miranda is ready to date outside of royalty! But let's not scrap the \"charming\" part just yet, yes? A girl has standards.",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_KALE": "KALE, TELL US: WHAT DO YOU LOOK FOR IN A FRIEND?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_KALE": "Well, I'm not into the whole \"seduction game\", or whatever people call it... I appreciate it when my friends aren't thinking about that 24/7. I'm more of a \"hobbies\" guy... so I guess I'm looking for someone who wants to hang out and play some co-op games!",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_MAMIMI": "MAMIMI, TELL US: WHAT IS YOUR TYPE?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_MAMIMI": "Competitive gaming is a big part of my life. I don't necessarily need someone to match my hardcore energy; but I wouldn't mind finding a Player 2 to my Player 1.",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_SCOTT": "SCOTT, TELL US: WHAT DO YOU LOOK FOR IN A FRIEND?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_SCOTT": "What do you mean? I like people in general! I believe you can make friends with almost anyone if you make the effort to get to know them.",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_VERA": "VERA, TELL US: WHAT IS YOUR TYPE?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_VERA": "What a generic and stupid question. I don't like people who ask stupid questions. Be less stupid. Thanks.",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_VERAVALERIE": "VERA, TELL US: WHAT IS YOUR PLAN?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_VERAVALERIE": "I'd love to spend time with my family. And you look an awful lot like my sibling... but are you REALLY my sibling, or just a lame copycat? The best way to prove you're an Oberlin through and through is to display our signature cunning.",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_GERARD": "GERARD, TELL US: WHAT IS YOUR TYPE?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_GERARD": "My type, you say? What is this, a romcom? Pfffff... if I ever connect with someone, it'll be someone who doesn't try to add \"rom\" or \"com\" to my life. At most, we could hang out in the graveyard, or laugh at all those fools who believe in love.",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_FREEHUGS": "BRUCE, TELL US: WHAT IS YOUR TYPE?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_FREEHUGS": "Well, I certainly like people who aren't afraid of public displays of affection! I love hugs, but NOT the illegal ones. Those shady hug dealers are ruining the reputation of us huggers! Say no to crimes and no to illegal hugs!",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_FANZINE": "YANG YANG, TELL US: WHAT IS YOUR TYPE?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_FANZINE": "I'm a DIY gal: I love making stuff on my own! But it'd be nice to have someone to exchange cool ideas for zines and other art projects with. And who knows? Maybe collaborating on a fanzine could mean we end up having... a different type of collaboration. Get it?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_SUSANNE": "SUSANNE, TELL US: WHAT IS YOUR TYPE?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_SUSANNE": "DUMB QUESTION! I want someone who puts the pedal to the metal; someone who stops at nothing to see what's beyond the horizon; someone who'd challenge the gods to a race and MAKE THEM EAT THEIR DUST!!!",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_PUPPET": "WYATT, TELL US: WHAT IS YOUR TYPE?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_PUPPET": "Haha, what a question! I love it. It's the perfect excuse to play a little game, don'tcha think? Let's see... I don't like [NUMBERS], so my \"type\" would be someone who could avoid those numbers AT ALL COSTS. Are you game?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_ZORRITO": "YI FENG, TELL US: WHAT IS YOUR TYPE?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_ZORRITO": "I like the idea of leaving love to chance. Of course, I'd appreciate getting to know you, but I'd also like to see an undeniable sign that we're meant to be. What if it was a sort of fateful, lucky number? Something like... [NUMBERS]?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_FAITH": "FAITH, TELL US: WHAT DO YOU LOOK FOR IN A FRIEND?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_FAITH": "I spend half my time risking my life in adventures with world-ending stakes. I guess that's why I like being around people who can appreciate a low-stakes life: drink some tea, pet a cat, and having nice conversations. Maybe someone who could enjoy discussing spells, charms and the like?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_TENGU": "NANASE, TELL US: WHAT IS YOUR TYPE?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TENGU": "I do enjoy people with a taste for literature. It doesn't need to be sci-fi, although I wouldn't complain if that's the case! Maybe even someone to join me in my brainstorming sessions? That'd be appealing! But preferably someone who's not just a quiet bookworm: I like people with a sharp tongue, who can hold a conversation and challenge me to a duel of wits... and pick-up lines, if it goes well.",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_TITLE_COSPLAYFIXER": "SASHA, TELL US: WHAT IS YOUR TYPE?",
		"DAT_PHONENPCINFO_COSPLAYFIXER": "Well, most of my interests could be summed up as \"nerds and crafts.\" So I'd say I'd enjoy the company of someone who's very into pop culture, just like myself. Also, my passion for cosplay has made me value much more people who have passions that involve inventiveness and craftiness.",

